WEBVTT

00:00:49.520 --> 00:00:50.120
Hong Xiu

00:00:52.040 --> 00:00:53.200
Madam Zhang had no heirs

00:00:54.360 --> 00:00:55.360
Our child

00:00:56.160 --> 00:00:58.440
died in the womb for no reason again

00:01:01.200 --> 00:01:02.920
The various reasons for this

00:01:03.760 --> 00:01:05.400
I am well aware of

00:01:06.920 --> 00:01:08.120
You have suffered

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:11.520
Now

00:01:12.440 --> 00:01:13.400
Madam Zhang has passed away

00:01:14.520 --> 00:01:16.040
Everything, absolutely everything

00:01:16.680 --> 00:01:18.120
is all in the past

00:01:19.560 --> 00:01:20.440
From now on

00:01:21.280 --> 00:01:21.720
you

00:01:22.120 --> 00:01:22.800
Hong Xiu

00:01:23.560 --> 00:01:25.760
will be the mistress of my Li Manor

00:01:37.560 --> 00:01:38.680
I know

00:01:39.560 --> 00:01:42.040
you still hold resentment in your heart

00:01:43.320 --> 00:01:45.040
Are you still angry with me?

00:01:48.960 --> 00:01:49.960
These past few days

00:01:50.920 --> 00:01:52.080
the matter of the Ghost Infant

00:01:52.920 --> 00:01:55.120
must have tormented you to no end

00:01:56.840 --> 00:01:57.560
I know

00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:01.360
Jin'er was my child too

00:02:02.040 --> 00:02:03.320
My heart aches for him as well

00:02:03.320 --> 00:02:04.800
I couldn't bear to lose him either

00:02:09.920 --> 00:02:11.120
Rest assured

00:02:12.680 --> 00:02:13.960
Whoever it was

00:02:14.560 --> 00:02:16.000
that disturbed Jin'er's body

00:02:17.200 --> 00:02:18.800
I will investigate to the very end

00:02:20.640 --> 00:02:21.720
I, Li Niangu

00:02:22.920 --> 00:02:25.640
will make them pay with blood

00:02:38.280 --> 00:02:39.000
Hong Xiu

00:02:41.520 --> 00:02:42.200
Hong Xiu

00:03:12.480 --> 00:03:14.360
Time of death was three hours ago

00:03:14.680 --> 00:03:15.360
At 10:00 PM

00:03:15.760 --> 00:03:17.040
The fatal wound is in the center of the back

00:03:17.400 --> 00:03:17.920
A stab wound

00:03:18.360 --> 00:03:19.160
piercing the heart

00:03:20.560 --> 00:03:21.080
Lord Li

00:03:22.400 --> 00:03:23.560
When did you arrive here?

00:03:24.640 --> 00:03:25.240
I...

00:03:25.800 --> 00:03:26.840
Around 11 PM

00:03:32.640 --> 00:03:33.840
In a mere hour

00:03:35.480 --> 00:03:36.720
To kill someone

00:03:36.840 --> 00:03:37.760
behead them

00:03:39.040 --> 00:03:41.440
and then clean up the scene

00:03:42.120 --> 00:03:42.880
is absolutely impossible

00:03:45.520 --> 00:03:46.520
You mean

00:03:47.080 --> 00:03:48.400
this is not the crime scene

00:03:50.880 --> 00:03:51.800
Who

00:03:51.960 --> 00:03:52.600
or what

00:03:53.160 --> 00:03:54.240
could have lured her out?

00:03:54.800 --> 00:03:55.760
And lured her to where?

00:04:18.520 --> 00:04:20.240
Something so important to you

00:04:21.040 --> 00:04:22.240
where would you keep it?

00:04:36.920 --> 00:04:37.320
No

00:05:09.360 --> 00:05:12.440
"If you want the truth, come to the alley in Changsheng Fang"

00:05:13.680 --> 00:05:14.400
Go to Changsheng Fang

00:05:16.040 --> 00:05:16.400
Guiyi

00:05:17.000 --> 00:05:17.840
Go back to Dali Temple and get help

00:05:18.160 --> 00:05:18.960
Transport the body back

00:05:19.440 --> 00:05:19.720
Yes

00:05:20.520 --> 00:05:21.040
Lord Li

00:05:22.240 --> 00:05:23.240
Until the matter is clarified

00:05:23.600 --> 00:05:24.480
please remain in your manor

00:05:25.920 --> 00:05:26.320
Yes

00:06:28.360 --> 00:06:29.520
Judging by the footprints

00:06:30.120 --> 00:06:32.200
it is the same person who stole the infant's body

00:06:33.320 --> 00:06:34.160
First it was Madam Zhang

00:06:34.360 --> 00:06:35.160
Then Hong Xiu

00:06:35.960 --> 00:06:36.520
Do you think

00:06:36.880 --> 00:06:38.920
who the killer is ultimately targeting?

00:06:42.400 --> 00:06:42.800
What?

00:06:43.440 --> 00:06:45.280
Even our Tang Dynasty's top detective

00:06:46.320 --> 00:06:47.040
is stumped?

00:06:48.080 --> 00:06:49.120
Regarding Madam Zhang's death

00:06:49.560 --> 00:06:50.840
Li Niangu's attitude is a puzzle

00:06:51.480 --> 00:06:52.640
It wasn't until Hong Xiu was killed

00:06:52.680 --> 00:06:53.480
that he reported the case

00:06:54.680 --> 00:06:56.280
Li Niangu must be hiding a secret

00:06:56.840 --> 00:06:58.360
The killer is forcing him to reveal it

00:06:59.440 --> 00:07:00.440
Madam Zhang's body

00:07:00.880 --> 00:07:02.000
before the burial

00:07:02.800 --> 00:07:03.400
needs to be examined in detail

00:07:18.760 --> 00:07:19.480
I found something.

00:07:19.880 --> 00:07:20.920
I opened Madam Zhang's stomach.

00:07:21.360 --> 00:07:22.640
And found traces of Phantom Mind Poison.

00:07:27.440 --> 00:07:28.920
She must have been taking Phantom Mind Poison for a long time.

00:07:28.920 --> 00:07:30.360
Causing her to live in constant fear.

00:07:30.800 --> 00:07:31.800
Seeing the ghosts in her mind.

00:07:32.520 --> 00:07:33.320
As expected.

00:07:35.280 --> 00:07:36.960
Someone who knew where the infants were buried.

00:07:37.120 --> 00:07:38.520
Could only be someone from the manor.

00:07:38.720 --> 00:07:42.120
Someone in this manor who could dig up a grave overnight...

00:07:42.120 --> 00:07:43.400
...and fill it back up again.

00:07:43.400 --> 00:07:45.280
Must be a strong young man.

00:07:45.400 --> 00:07:47.240
Skilled in using knives to dismember bodies.

00:07:47.280 --> 00:07:48.960
And had access to the Madam's meals.

00:07:49.160 --> 00:07:50.800
Meeting all these conditions...

00:07:51.000 --> 00:07:52.240
That person can only be...

00:07:55.000 --> 00:07:55.800
The cook.

00:07:57.560 --> 00:07:58.080
My Lord.

00:08:02.080 --> 00:08:02.560
What is it?

00:08:03.240 --> 00:08:04.400
A night watchman came to report a case.

00:08:04.920 --> 00:08:06.080
Claiming he saw someone last night...

00:08:06.480 --> 00:08:07.920
A Headless ghost holding a human head.

00:08:08.320 --> 00:08:08.880
What?

00:08:11.000 --> 00:08:11.680
The man said...

00:08:11.840 --> 00:08:14.160
It was the head of Qin Shitou, who was executed five days ago.

00:08:14.320 --> 00:08:14.920
He recognized it.

00:08:16.600 --> 00:08:18.680
Qin Shitou was a servant at Li Niangu's manor.

00:08:18.880 --> 00:08:19.840
For attempting to assassinate Li Niangu...

00:08:20.160 --> 00:08:20.960
He was sentenced to beheading.

00:08:21.440 --> 00:08:22.400
Li Niangu again.

00:08:22.800 --> 00:08:23.480
What time last night?

00:08:24.080 --> 00:08:24.520
9:00 PM.

00:08:25.280 --> 00:08:25.880
9:00 PM.

00:08:28.600 --> 00:08:30.400
Hong Xiu died at 10:00 PM.

00:08:31.760 --> 00:08:33.720
Li Niangu went there around 11 PM.

00:08:37.520 --> 00:08:38.840
Do you suspect Hong Xiu...

00:08:39.600 --> 00:08:41.240
Was killed by this walking corpse of Qin Shitou?

00:08:42.680 --> 00:08:45.080
All the key evidence points to Hong Xiu.

00:08:46.280 --> 00:08:47.760
So, between this killer and Hong Xiu...

00:08:48.320 --> 00:08:49.360
What exactly is the connection?

00:08:52.280 --> 00:08:52.640
Guiyi.

00:08:53.160 --> 00:08:55.520
Bring me all the files on the Qin Shitou case.

00:08:56.560 --> 00:08:56.840
Yes, sir.

00:08:58.920 --> 00:08:59.560
Acting Vice Minister.

00:08:59.880 --> 00:09:02.000
There was indeed a cook in my manor.

00:09:02.880 --> 00:09:03.640
His height...

00:09:03.920 --> 00:09:05.200
As Investigator Shen Tu said...

00:09:05.400 --> 00:09:06.560
Was about five feet seven inches.

00:09:06.880 --> 00:09:07.880
His name is Liu Mu.

00:09:08.720 --> 00:09:11.280
But he resigned due to illness and returned home a few days ago.

00:09:11.440 --> 00:09:13.840
So we haven't found a suitable cook since.

00:09:14.040 --> 00:09:16.080
This place has been empty ever since.

00:09:16.800 --> 00:09:18.400
When did he start working at your manor?

00:09:19.280 --> 00:09:20.200
Approximately...

00:09:20.880 --> 00:09:21.560
Half a year ago.

00:09:21.880 --> 00:09:22.960
A cook.

00:09:23.080 --> 00:09:23.680
Lord Li.

00:09:23.960 --> 00:09:25.160
Why do you remember so clearly?

00:09:26.000 --> 00:09:26.960
You may not know, My Lord.

00:09:27.640 --> 00:09:29.400
My wife loved Huaiyang Cuisine.

00:09:29.760 --> 00:09:31.520
I searched for a long time to find this cook.

00:09:31.840 --> 00:09:33.920
He was indeed quite skilled at making Huaiyang Cuisine.

00:09:34.360 --> 00:09:35.520
So he left a deep impression on me.

00:09:37.120 --> 00:09:38.520
I just didn't expect...

00:09:38.720 --> 00:09:40.200
That I had invited a thief into my home.

00:09:40.480 --> 00:09:41.240
I heard...

00:09:41.680 --> 00:09:44.480
That you also met Hong Xiu half a year ago.

00:09:44.640 --> 00:09:45.080
Is that so?

00:09:45.720 --> 00:09:46.200
That is correct.

00:09:46.840 --> 00:09:47.280
However...

00:09:47.720 --> 00:09:50.240
Hong Xiu and Liu Mu shouldn't have any connection.

00:10:05.880 --> 00:10:06.640
This is...

00:10:09.400 --> 00:10:11.440
My wife and I have never had children.

00:10:11.800 --> 00:10:13.160
So we often get some herbal medicine

00:10:13.160 --> 00:10:14.280
to improve our health.

00:10:19.880 --> 00:10:20.720
It's Phantom Mind Poison.

00:10:29.720 --> 00:10:30.360
By the way, my lord,

00:10:32.400 --> 00:10:33.960
I need to ask you about someone.

00:10:34.600 --> 00:10:35.120
Please speak.

00:10:36.000 --> 00:10:36.720
Qin Shitou.

00:10:37.920 --> 00:10:39.280
Qin Shitou.

00:10:41.840 --> 00:10:43.440
There was indeed such a person in the manor.

00:10:43.960 --> 00:10:45.320
Why does the Master ask about that thief?

00:10:45.880 --> 00:10:48.120
Rumors spread this morning that he has become a headless walking corpse.

00:10:48.880 --> 00:10:50.880
Naturally, I must ask your honor about the situation.

00:10:51.280 --> 00:10:53.640
Qin Shitou was originally a groom in the manor.

00:10:54.080 --> 00:10:56.320
I discovered he had been embezzling fodder money for years.

00:10:56.400 --> 00:10:57.320
He stole a countless amount.

00:10:57.760 --> 00:10:58.880
I wanted to consider our past relationship

00:10:59.480 --> 00:11:01.000
and hoped he would repent.

00:11:01.400 --> 00:11:03.160
Unexpectedly, he tried to assassinate me.

00:11:03.800 --> 00:11:05.200
So I reported him to the Magistrate's office.

00:11:05.680 --> 00:11:07.400
He was convicted of embezzlement and attempted assassination.

00:11:08.040 --> 00:11:09.160
Later, he was sentenced to beheading.

00:11:13.360 --> 00:11:15.960
What about Qin Shitou's family?

00:11:18.520 --> 00:11:18.920
Yes.

00:11:19.880 --> 00:11:22.760
He had a wife and a pair of children.

00:11:23.640 --> 00:11:24.400
After the incident,

00:11:24.640 --> 00:11:27.400
she took the children and left Chang'an City.

00:11:28.800 --> 00:11:29.240
That is all.

00:11:30.880 --> 00:11:31.440
Old Yao, let's go.

00:12:00.160 --> 00:12:00.440
Oh no.

00:12:00.760 --> 00:12:01.160
Look.

00:12:03.600 --> 00:12:04.880
Could it really be a walking corpse?

00:12:05.760 --> 00:12:06.560
Why is this happening?

00:12:07.400 --> 00:12:09.640
Didn't you say everything was settled and foolproof?

00:12:10.240 --> 00:12:11.920
I only used his children to perform the Human Foundation Sacrifice for you.

00:12:12.280 --> 00:12:13.160
Why was he beheaded?

00:12:13.400 --> 00:12:14.640
Don't you know that yourself?

00:12:15.520 --> 00:12:16.760
Tell me, why did you kill him?

00:12:16.920 --> 00:12:17.840
You said it yourself.

00:12:17.840 --> 00:12:19.000
You wanted to take his boy-girl twins

00:12:19.360 --> 00:12:20.720
to create a human pile for suppression.

00:12:20.720 --> 00:12:21.880
Where did that suppression go?

00:12:24.160 --> 00:12:25.280
Since half a year ago,

00:12:25.640 --> 00:12:27.240
after the first boy was used as a human pile,

00:12:27.520 --> 00:12:28.560
not only have I not been promoted,

00:12:28.720 --> 00:12:30.400
but strange things have happened one after another.

00:12:31.480 --> 00:12:31.920
Nowadays,

00:12:32.560 --> 00:12:33.480
first it was the Ghost Infant,

00:12:33.960 --> 00:12:35.240
turning our Li Manor upside down

00:12:35.240 --> 00:12:36.560
and causing utter chaos.

00:12:37.520 --> 00:12:38.120
And then?

00:12:38.720 --> 00:12:41.800
Madam Zhang and Hong Xiu died inexplicably.

00:12:42.160 --> 00:12:43.400
Both of my wives are dead.

00:12:43.640 --> 00:12:44.160
If this goes on,

00:12:44.200 --> 00:12:45.320
everyone in Li Manor will be dead soon.

00:12:45.800 --> 00:12:47.880
Now some headless walking corpse has appeared.

00:12:48.320 --> 00:12:50.080
I gave you so much silver.

00:12:50.960 --> 00:12:52.440
Where did the money go?

00:12:52.960 --> 00:12:53.680
Could it be

00:12:54.040 --> 00:12:55.520
that you set up this scheme

00:12:55.960 --> 00:12:57.160
to murder me?

00:12:57.240 --> 00:12:58.120
What nonsense are you talking about?

00:12:59.280 --> 00:12:59.880
You are...

00:13:06.040 --> 00:13:07.080
Look, is that a person?

00:13:18.680 --> 00:13:19.640
Qin Shitou.

00:13:20.360 --> 00:13:21.720
Chopping the neck...

00:13:22.920 --> 00:13:24.800
hurts so much.